乔尼·米切尔、马丁·斯科塞斯和莱昂纳多·迪卡普里奥出席罗比·罗伯逊追悼会https://www.nme.com/news/music/joni-mitchell-martin-scorsese-and-leonardo-dicaprio-attend-robbie-robertson-memorial-3541393?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=joni-mitchell-martin-斯科塞斯和莱昂纳多迪卡普里奥出席罗比罗伯森纪念馆Kevin EG PerryThu, 16 Nov 2023 17:02:36 +0000 Film NewsMusic NewsNewsTV NewsMartin Scorsese https://www.nme.com/?p=3541393 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/ROBBIE_ROBERTSON_MEMORIAL_2000.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="2023 年 11 月 15 日，马丁·斯科塞斯 (Martin Scorsese) 在加利福尼亚州洛杉矶 The Village Studios 出席罗比·罗伯逊纪念音乐会。 （由 Rich Polk/Variety 拍摄，盖蒂图片社拍摄）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/ROBBIE_ROBERTSON_MEMORIAL_2000.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/ROBBIE_ROBERTSON_MEMORIAL_2000-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/ROBBIE_ROBERTSON_MEMORIAL_2000-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/ROBBIE_ROBERTSON_MEMORIAL_2000-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/ROBBIE_ROBERTSON_MEMORIAL_2000-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/ROBBIE_ROBERTSON_MEMORIAL_2000-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> 《花月杀手》导演在活动中发表了热情洋溢的悼词，其中还包括杰克逊·布朗、安吉拉·麦克拉斯基和杰森·伊斯贝尔的音乐致敬</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/joni-mitchell-martin-scorsese-and-leonardo-dicaprio-attend-robbie-robertson-memorial-3541393">乔尼·米切尔、马丁·斯科塞斯和莱昂纳多·迪卡普里奥参加罗比·罗伯逊追悼会的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/ROBBIE_ROBERTSON_MEMORIAL_2000.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="2023 年 11 月 15 日，马丁·斯科塞斯 (Martin Scorsese) 在加利福尼亚州洛杉矶 The Village Studios 出席罗比·罗伯逊纪念音乐会。 （由 Rich Polk/Variety 拍摄，盖蒂图片社拍摄）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/ROBBIE_ROBERTSON_MEMORIAL_2000.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/ROBBIE_ROBERTSON_MEMORIAL_2000-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/ROBBIE_ROBERTSON_MEMORIAL_2000-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/ROBBIE_ROBERTSON_MEMORIAL_2000-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/ROBBIE_ROBERTSON_MEMORIAL_2000-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/ROBBIE_ROBERTSON_MEMORIAL_2000-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>昨晚（11 月 15 日），<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/joni-mitchell">乔尼·米切尔 (Joni Mitchell)</a>和莱昂纳多·迪卡普里奥 (Leonardo DiCaprio) 等人齐聚一堂，庆祝已故<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/THE-BAND">乐队</a>吉他手兼创作歌手罗比·<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ROBBE-ROBERTSON">罗伯逊 (Robbie Robertson)</a>的生活和音乐。</p><ul><li> <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/film-interviews/martin-scorsese-killers-of-the-flower-moon-3516541"><strong>阅读更多：</strong>马丁·斯科塞斯的智慧：“我必须经历一切才能学习”</a></li></ul><p>纪念活动在罗伯逊长期居住的洛杉矶工作室老家 The Village 举行，导演马丁·斯科塞斯 (Martin Scorsese) 致以感人至深的悼念，杰克逊·布朗 (Jackson Browne)、公民·科普 (Citizen Cope)、安吉拉·麦克拉斯基 (Angela McCluskey) 等人表演了罗伯逊的音乐。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-band-robbie-robertson-has-died-aged-80-3480702">罗伯逊在长期患病后于8月9日去世</a>，享年80岁。</p><p>斯科塞斯和罗伯逊在拍摄乐队传奇音乐会电影<em>《最后的华尔兹》</em>时首次相识。斯科塞斯在悼词中说道：“我想，归根结底，这是一种双人组合。” “也就是说，两个人走到一起，做了一些他们自己不会做的事情。”</p><p>最初计划只是录制乐队 1976 年告别音乐会的现场录音，斯科塞斯和罗伯逊一起花了两年时间制作这部电影。 “罗比住在家里的那两年里，我们上的是非正式课程，”斯科塞斯回忆道。 “我上音乐课，他上电影课。他向我介绍了晦涩的布鲁斯音乐、福音音乐和神圣竖琴歌手。我向他介绍了萨姆·富勒的电影、帕索里尼的《Accattone》、《维斯康蒂》……我们真的分享了我们所喜欢的东西。” </p><figure id="attachment_3541401" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3541401" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3541401" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/ROBBIE_ROBERTSON_MEMORIAL_2000_2.jpg" alt="Leonardo DiCaprio at the Robbie Robertson Memorial Concert at The Village Studios on November 15, 2023 in Los Angeles, California. (Photo by Rich Polk/Variety via Getty Images)" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/ROBBIE_ROBERTSON_MEMORIAL_2000_2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/ROBBIE_ROBERTSON_MEMORIAL_2000_2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/ROBBIE_ROBERTSON_MEMORIAL_2000_2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/ROBBIE_ROBERTSON_MEMORIAL_2000_2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/ROBBIE_ROBERTSON_MEMORIAL_2000_2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/ROBBIE_ROBERTSON_MEMORIAL_2000_2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3541401" class="wp-caption-text"> Leonardo DiCaprio at the Robbie Robertson Memorial Concert at The Village Studios on November 15, 2023 in Los Angeles, California. (Photo by Rich Polk/Variety via Getty Images)</figcaption></figure><p> The pair continued to collaborate on films including 1980&#39;s <em>Raging Bull</em> , 1995&#39;s <em>Casino</em> and 2016&#39;s <em>Silence</em> . Scorsese recalled Robertson sending him four CDs full of musical suggestions for 2006&#39;s <em>The Departed</em> . The opening track was <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/DROPKICK-MURPHYS">Dropkick Murphy</a> &#39;s &#39;I&#39;m Shipping Up to Boston&#39;, which Scorsese ended up using repeatedly in the film.</p><p> Most recently, Robertson composed the music for Scorsese&#39;s <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/killers-of-the-flower-moon-review-martin-scorsese-3448518"><em>Killers of the Flower Moon</em></a> . A medley from the score was performed at the memorial by an orchestra conducted by Mark Graham. Other musical performances included Angela McCluskey singing &#39;Whispering Pines&#39;, Jackson Browne covering The Band&#39;s &#39;Caledonia Mission&#39; and a singalong finale of &#39;The Weight&#39; featuring Browne, Jason Isbell, Blake Mills and Tal Wilkenfeld.</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li> <strong>READ MORE: <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/film-interviews/the-bands-robbie-robertson-interview-once-were-brothers-2754474">The Band&#39;s Robbie Robertson: “If there was anything wrong with &#39;The Last Waltz&#39; it was that the cocaine wasn&#39;t very good”</a></strong></li></ul><p> Welcoming guests to the event, The Village Studios owner Jeff Greenberg recalled the effect Robertson could have on the band who came to record while he was around.</p><p> “Everybody who ever came here wanted to go so hi to Robbie,” he said. “&#39;Robbie, so-and-so&#39;s here, they want to see you.&#39; &#39;Sorry, tell them I&#39;m busy.&#39; Occasionally he would bestow his presence on people, like Elton John, Leon Russell or U2. One little group was here, I couldn&#39;t believe, he went down and say hi to Wolfmother. It was like they&#39;d been kissed on the forehead by God. They&#39;re still glowing.”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/film-interviews/martin-scorsese-killers-of-the-flower-moon-3516541">In a recent interview with <em>NME</em></a> , Scoresese looked back on his five decade friendship with Robertson.</p><p> “We knew each other for 50 years,” he said, “and so his last work is this music in the film. And he was indigenous too. I think his mother was from the Mohawk Nation, up in First Nations in Canada. And so it was a very special project for Rob to do.”</p><p> He added: “Every aspect of this film – the Osage culture, the baby namings, the funerals, the wedding, all these things were something I wanted to recreate. So we learn about these cultures and learn more about ourselves.”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-band-robbie-robertson-has-died-aged-80-3480702">Neil Diamond, Joni Mitchell and Bill Clinton were among those to pay tribute</a> to Robertson when he passed, with <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bob-dylan-pays-tribute-to-lifelong-friend-robbie-robertson-3482042">Bob Dylan also honouring his “life-long friend</a> “.</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/joni-mitchell-martin-scorsese-and-leonardo-dicaprio-attend-robbie-robertson-memorial-3541393">Joni Mitchell, Martin Scorsese and Leonardo DiCaprio attend Robbie Robertson memorial</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
